<i> the Jaguar Preserve
 had taken off.</i>

00:13:53.732 --> 00:13:55.868
<i> Eco-tourism was booming</i>

00:13:55.868 --> 00:13:59.137
<i> but it didn't seem to relate
 to the jaguar.</i>

00:13:59.137 --> 00:14:03.175
<i> The way people treated jaguars
 and other animals,</i>

00:14:03.175 --> 00:14:05.377
<i> the way people viewed them</i>

00:14:05.377 --> 00:14:09.614
<i> was still as
 a recreational outlet.</i>

00:14:09.614 --> 00:14:11.483
<i> Maybe they didn't kill them,</i>

00:14:11.483 --> 00:14:14.953
<i>so we played with them instead.</i>

00:14:14.953 --> 00:14:17.255
In 1999, I called together

00:14:17.255 --> 00:14:18.957
