it was less than 25 people.

00:14:25.497 --> 00:14:28.333
The point was to try to get
all the knowledge

00:14:28.333 --> 00:14:30.702
of what we knew about jaguars.

00:14:30.702 --> 00:14:34.005
Where did jaguars live
to our knowledge at that time?

00:14:34.005 --> 00:14:37.776
<i> In 1999 we were able to
 determine about 51</i>

00:14:37.776 --> 00:14:41.046
<i> what's called JCUs,
 Jaguar Conservation Units.</i>

00:14:41.046 --> 00:14:44.650
<i> Places where we knew
 jaguars lived and bred.</i>

00:14:44.650 --> 00:14:48.153
<i> By later in 2000 it went up to
 almost a 100.</i>

