00:14:57.762 --> 00:15:00.365
in different kinds of
habitat types.

00:15:00.365 --> 00:15:04.803
So save just the highest
priority jaguar populations

00:15:04.803 --> 00:15:08.540
in different kinds of systems.
That seemed great.

00:15:08.540 --> 00:15:11.676
<i> At this meeting there
 were a group of geneticists.</i>

00:15:11.676 --> 00:15:13.444
<i> We were gonna use DNA</i>

00:15:13.444 --> 00:15:15.513
<i> and figure out how many races</i>

