where there is no individual
races of that animal

00:16:06.798 --> 00:16:10.936
which has been
defined through genetics.

00:16:10.936 --> 00:16:14.006
<i> What it meant is that these
 places where we thought were</i>

00:16:14.006 --> 00:16:16.875
<i> outside of jaguar range
 it was all important.</i>

00:16:16.875 --> 00:16:18.277
<i> Forget triage</i>

